{"tid":953701,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人咁得閒，點解唔推一間野徹底打殘支那喜茶？","createTime":"2018-12-24T06:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T17:38:47.000Z","uid":1477,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc0aa417d7c6a8b4aa2c7a30ccaaaea3c502eb9","tid":953701,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post 係到屌屌屌<br />\n拎人地法國黃背心同香港人排支那喜茶黎比<br />\n做乜鳩柒，成陣自卑酸臭味湧撚哂出黎<br />\n哦，崇日崇洋就叫崇優<br />\n支那野做得好就叫左劣幣驅良幣，而家啲香港人品味差<br />\n香港人幾時變到咁撚廢？<br />\n以前就靠做好野黎立招牌，而家就好似拋一句支那化學劑就贏哂咁<br />\n講真啦，呢d 濕鳩飲品，傳入香港都好撚多年啦，有邊間係香港自己打響名堂，逆輸入返去台灣/支那？<br />\n貢茶，天仁，老虎堂，幸福堂等等<br />\n人地係台灣百花齊放，你地就話人地一日到黑飲化學劑<br />\n香港人唔撚飲汽水咩屌<br />\n真仔好撚嘔心，而家部份反支反到唔識點反，剩係諗點反又唔諗住點自強，咁咪同垃圾滿清一樣囉"},{"pid":"8972746ff9be15816cfac75311e85fea25e0d58b","tid":953701,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"依家先知cc台係集支那人劣根性於一身？"},{"pid":"39c98ad2b498c35d432d5d3a4b146dd32396eba8","tid":953701,"uid":66810,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"喜茶叫做得好#<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aae45aa21f15396f7a92955c41a65c623f14a1","tid":953701,"uid":106426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55e886688ffa624cee971c88339fe35cb2f3040a","tid":953701,"uid":147047,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:42:35.000Z","msg":"天仁完勝"},{"pid":"79952fa0a79023d36d0f2f311ea0330d8cd01db1","tid":953701,"uid":1477,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"39c98ad2b498c35d432d5d3a4b146dd32396eba8","tid":953701,"uid":66810,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"喜茶叫做得好#<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2